responded: Here is the patch to fix the use-after-free by returning a pointer to the global uninitialized zval (`&EG(uninitialized_zval)`) after freeing the reference in `zend_assign_to_variable`:

```diff
--- a/Zend/zend_execute.h
+++ b/Zend/zend_execute.h
@@ -160,10 +160,14 @@
